Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.01,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 3: KESEHARIAN YANG KEMBALI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:40.02,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,SELANJUTNYA: PENYIHIR TINGKAT RAJA AIR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di hadapanku ada sesosok dewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewi yang berbaring dengan lembut\Nseperti sang Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia adalah sosok mulia,\Nmaka tidak boleh lupa memberi hormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pinggang tanpa lekukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh yang membuat orang bertanya-tanya,\Nbukankah terlalu belia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang terlihat di dadanya,\Napakah itu mata suci?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak yang terjadi di antara kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku bahagia bisa terikat\Ndengan Roxy seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, gawat, waktu kami tidak banyak\Ndi pagi hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus kubangunkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roxy, ayo bangun, sudah pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa? Kenapa memasang muka\Nseperti sedang kecewa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin memandang lekat tubuh\NMaster Roxy di tempat yang lebih terang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ih, kita harus cepat berangkat,\Nyang lain pasti sudah bangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Sylphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini Lucy sehat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkebalikan denganku yang mudah khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucy tumbuh begitu sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisi Sylphy setelah persalinan juga bagus,\Nibu dan anaknya sama-sama sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini putriku manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa bisa semanis ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti karena mamanya juga manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar. Terima kasih, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Roxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Roxy, kemarin Rudy bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, ah, a-anu, dia sangat baik padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rudy juga begitu lembut...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Norn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedikit merangkum lagi cerita Ruijerd,\Nbisa tidak Kakak membacanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buku yang sedang kubuat untuk\Nmemulihkan nama baik suku Superdia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekarang lebih banyak ditulis Norn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski belum terlalu bagus,\Ndia begitu semangat menulisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa hasilnya akan lebih menarik\Ndaripada aku yang menulis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kunantikan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, ini Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sekarang setelah beberapa bulan\Nkembali ke Sharia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ingatan Zenith masih belum kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perlahan memang terlihat perubahannya,\Ntapi sekarang cuma bisa memantau kondisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sarapan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sarapan sudah siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Kakak dan Nyonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sarapan hari ini apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sarapan hari ini kurang lebih\Nsama seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan malas menjelaskan menu sarapan pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sup kacang arab dan roti gandum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu susu kuda yang penuh nutrisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rudeus, Nyonya Sylphiette,\NNyonya Roxy, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Lilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha dan Lilia tetap melakukan tugas rumah\Nseperti selama ini sebagai pembantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski Aisha sering dimarahi\Nkarena terlalu semangat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi keduanya kelihatan menikmati sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami memang pernah saling terpisah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi keluargaku berhasil\Nberkumpul lagi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini aku sudah cukup bahagia dengan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, selamat makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini aku dan Sylphy\Nkembali masuk sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, bukan cuma kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, Roxy sudah kamu kenalkan\Nke teman-teman di sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat merekomendasikan Master\Nuntuk jadi pengajar di akademi sihir,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sudah mengenalkan kehebatannya\Nke teman-teman sekalian mengantar keliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya Guru adalah orang yang mulia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengetahui kemuliaannya itu\Njelas akan jadi nilai plus untuk semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khas Rudy sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang dikenalkan ke banyak orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:06:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, meski menyebutku sebagai masternya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rudy tidak bilang kalau aku istrinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rudy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf, Roxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, cintaku sayangku,\Naku betulan mencintaimu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Te-Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Rudy, kamu tidak mau bilang itu padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu aku juga mencintai Sylphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat kucinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ih, Rudy!\N- Keren, Bos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mantap, Ahli Rawa!\N- Jangan begitu kalau di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak memalukan, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku ke arah sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, Norn semangat belajarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak, hari ini aku pulang lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Norn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Norn sangat tenar, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Norn adalah anak manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat terasa kalau dia sudah\Nberusaha keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ingin menyemangatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai kakak,\Naku senang kalau adikku tenar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, tidak akan kubiarkan kalau\Ncowok-cowok itu berani colek-colek Norn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan kurelakan adikku\Nke orang yang tidak jelas asal-usulnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar begitu, kan, Ayah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pe-Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah saya tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini Rudeus aktif kembali\Nmasuk ke akademi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, kemarin baru sekadar memberi salam,\Ntapi mulai hari ini
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya jadi murid merepotkan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga mohon bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roxy juga harus mulai mengajar hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, apa kamu merasa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roxy yang dulu bilang\Ntidak ingin jadi pengajar,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekarang banyak berubah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, saya sendiri juga kaget.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu itu saya terlalu merasa besar diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi, sekarang saya merasa sedikit mengerti\Nrasa senangnya mengajari sesuatu ke orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon bantuannya, Bu Guru Roxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku duluan ke kelas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walah, ternyata aku yang pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Bos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, meong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lihat, lo, Bos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak sekali hidup Bos, pagi-pagi sudah\Nberangkat sekolah bawa dua cewek.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bajingan sekali mencampakkan kami\Ndan bawa istri kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan lulus tahun ini,\Nmungkin saatnya cari pasangan, meong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, tuh.\NTahun ini harus duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat cari cowok lalu pulang\Nke kampung halaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo cari cowok yang oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal selama ini bilang\Nkalau itu merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sepertinya mereka iri padaku\Nkarena punya dua madu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ada Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Tuan Besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Zanoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi juga, Julie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Guru datang ke kelas,\Nberarti mulai hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, kita bisa meneliti sama-sama lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pas sekali kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah ini ada yang ingin kutunjukkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasil penelitianku selama setengah tahun ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baiklah, akan kutunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu, kalau kamu datang ke sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berarti sementara ini\Ntidak akan ke mana-mana, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti penelitiannya bisa diteruskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rudeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Kak Cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lize bilang kamu juga ikut pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa malah tidak datang\Nmenemuiku untuk beri salam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku sudah coba datang, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya sedang sibuk sama Elinalise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Begitu, ya?!\NApa boleh buat kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga yang salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kalau anakmu sudah lahir,\Nkenapa tidak bilang apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kamu sibuk merawat anak,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi, belakangan ini bukannya kamu\Nseperti menghindariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin benar begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa dirinya yang pemeluk agama Milis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak akan begitu menyukaiku\Nyang punya dua istri ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau malah, ada alasannya kamu\Ntidak ingin bertemu denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sebenarnya aku pu...\N- Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, duduk di kursi masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Roxy Migurdia Greyrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini dia akan ditugaskan\Nsebagai pengajar di Akademi Sihir Ranoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk sementara aku akan ikut membantu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia akan jadi wali kelas kalian\Nyang baru,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi tolong bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin banyak yang sudah berkenalan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku adalah istri kedua dari\NRudeus Greyrat yang ada di situ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:12:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara interaksi antara guru dan murid\Nkurasa akan berbeda,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mohon bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Istri kedua, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rudeus, apa kamu ini tidak punya\Nyang namanya prinsip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya, kurasa diriku memang\Nkurang di bagian itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu aku memberkatimu karena kau bilang\Nakan mencintai Sylphy seorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku benar-benar\Nberterima kasih untuk itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang, aku tidak akan berkata lebih jauh\Nkarena dirimu bukan pemeluk agama Milis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, justru akan kuberkati saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terkadang bertemu adikmu di gereja kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang ingin jadi pasutri yang rukun\Ndan mesra seperti Kakak dan Kak Sylphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa yang dia katakan padamu\Nsaat membawa istri yang kedua?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia hampir tiap hari mendoakan\Nkepulanganmu serta ayahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dirimu bisa pulang hidup-hidup\Npastilah sangat membahagiakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi, kini hanya dirimulah tempat dia\Nbisa bergantung setelah kehilangan ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sebaiknya dirimu lebih\Nmemikirkan perasaan Norn lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menambah pasangan terlalu banyak\Nitu tidak baik, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Kak Cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Rudeus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi Kakak sudah menemani Norn, ya.\NTerima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma menemaninya ngobrol\Nkarena ketemu di gereja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, anak sekecil dia\Njangan dibiarkan jalan sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sekitar sini memang aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, masuk ke gang kecil sedikit saja\Nbisa diculik, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, akan kuingat baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar? Kamu ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, sudah, bukankah cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa kembali hidup-hidup saja sudah syukur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, dia sendiri kelihatannya\Nsudah tahu kesalahannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kumaafkan dosamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewa Milis memang Maha Pengampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah dengar dari Lize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawanmu sampai bisa membuatmu\Nkehilangan sebelah tangan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawanku hydra yang kebal pada sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebal sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja kalau dirimu kesulitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali bisa kau kalahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ada rombongan Ayah di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami memang bisa menang,\Ntapi yang hilang juga besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar, Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong lihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benda yang tadi kubilang di kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasil dari penelitian kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong kemarikan tangan kiri Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}O-Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayak mau jatuh, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantranya adalah,\N"Wahai Bumi, jadilah tanganku."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong coba dirapalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai Bumi, jadilah tanganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerak! Ini bisa gerak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini, Rudeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali!\NBisa terasa sampai ujung jarinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan sihir yang bisa bergerak\Nsesuai keinginan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini berhasil kubuat dari menganalisis\Npatung automaton dengan bantuan Tuan Cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dengan ini, pasti bisa membuat patung\Nyang bisa menahan kekuatan superku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ingin pakai tenaga, ini akan menguat\Nsebanyak daya sihir yang diberikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu marah sama yang tadi, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami belum tahu bisa dipakai atau tidak,\Nkalau tidak punya tangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sepertinya tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, bisa tidak aku pakai sihir\Ndengan tangan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa tidak, segera lepaskan tanganmu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kalau begitu, mari kita uji coba!\N- Jangan diremas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada duel lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, coba sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kumulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penggunaan sihir saat dikenakan\Nsepertinya juga tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru memang hebat!\NMengesankan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini penemuan yang luar biasa!\NAku betulan kaget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bila berkenan, akan kuberikan\Ntangan itu untuk Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang masih purwarupa,\Ntapi masih mending daripada tidak punya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apalagi kalau dibantu Guru dan Tuan Cliff,\Npasti bisa segera membuat yang serupa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh iya, alat sihir ini apa sudah ada namanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, masih belum ada namanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diriku dan Tuan Cliff memang\Ntidak ahli dalam memberi nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau sekalian saja\Nkamu yang menamainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, silakan dinamai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ambil dari nama kalian berdua,\Nbagaimana kalau Tangan Imitasi Zaliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada namamu, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, aku tidak terlibat soalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya tidak bisa disebut\Nkalau tidak terlibat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kalau begitu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita namai tangan itu\NTangan Imitasi Zaliff versi satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang, Kakak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau makan dulu? Mandi dulu?\NAtau justru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mau diriku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, biar kupilih Aisha saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kitik, kitik, kitik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diserang Kakak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan palsu ini alat sihir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sepertinya ini hasil dari\Npenelitian Zanoba dan Kak Cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali, bisa bergerak\Nseperti tangan sungguhan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bisa bergerak seperti ini,\Nkegiatan sehari-hari rasanya bisa diatasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, dengan ini aku bisa\Nmenikmati kalian berdua sepenuh hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ih, Rudy ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, kamu pegang apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak, bikin malu tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan malam...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan malamnya sudah siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan malam hari ini kurang lebih\Nsama seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh banyak yang terjadi setelah\Nbencana teleportasi Wilayah Fittoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Petualangan di Benua Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perpisahan dengan Eris.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengobati penyakitku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menikah dengan Sylphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bertemu lagi dengan Roxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyelamatkan Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski ada juga yang hilang karena itu semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, keseharian yang biasanya\Nsudah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang, akan kuhargai\N"keseharian biasa" ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah aku mendapat kembali\Nkeseharian yang damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini pun berdoa dengan khidmat\Nseperti ini.
